name: Floppy Disks 5 x 5
description: An homage to the wonders of the Floppy Disk. A relic now, but indispensable back when Dad's mate from work was the single source of all my PC games - every one of them on at least 2 3.5" floppy disks. Something that I think about occasionally when I can't be arsed to find a USB Key and email gigantic files from one household PC to the other. Procedurally randomized to keep it fresh :: shig_nft 2021
